*"Šteta* je što nismo ranije shvatili da će to biti problem." (It's a pity that we didn't realize earlier that it will be a problem.)

*"Nažalost,* *šteta* je već učinjena." (Unfortunately, the damage is already done.)

*"Šteta* je što nismo mogli da dobijemo bolji rezultat." (It's a shame that we couldn't get a better result.)

*"Štetno* je ako neko ne poštuje pravila." (It's harmful if someone doesn't respect the rules.)

*"Štetno* je što ljudi ne razumeju važnost zaštite životne sredine." (It's detrimental that people don't understand the importance of environmental protection.)